[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man charged over girls sex assault in Burnley

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been charged by police investigating the sexual assault of two schoolgirls in Burnley.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police launched an investigation after two girls aged 13 and 14 were assaulted in separate incidents in the town centre on Tuesday and Wednesday.
A 24-year-old man from Burnley has been charged with sexual assault and false imprisonment, Lancashire Police said.
He is due to appear before magistrates in Burnley on Monday.
